{"tid":1234303,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不如頂多一個星期，等侵侵多啲籌碼同雜傾講數","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:57:08.000Z","uid":53515,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"323b1b04e69c9b6a954e50e5a104d5cd114bc325","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"28/6就係 我哋挨多一個星期。<br />\n<br />\n侵侵已經講明會同雜總講及香港問題<br />\n<br />\n雖然可能只係換來侵侵講多幾隻字，但依個係目前<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔流血 不被捕 香港人成本最低</span>嘅情況下其中一個有效嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n如果真做 就討論下星期遊行有咩訴求 試下傾個共識出嚟"},{"pid":"c26e746b8263a6be2e8db4b1d6f809437ed3b2e6","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"04439da444035e7f5c4e27e781025dee0709a7b8","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:39:23.000Z","msg":"黑警不惜開槍都要保護議會<br />\n<br />\n真正stop港共係外國嘅聲明 尤其美國研究取清香獨立關稅 港共第2日就跪咗 侵侵一隻字就好似大炮咁有威力 我哋香港都可以流少啲血<br />\n<br />\n如果下星期大家有決心嚟多次 我必到"},{"pid":"4da9a34e8dc5a86bd37aa4d00e1be86e5b54a766","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a91a10bb16aa2d4c559427ee7c860d80fc7e909","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e82cf790b89d96e08aa32af6c47ee187893d23b9","tid":1234303,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:40:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c42d28b8c3f9a17b89ff3d157955caeb7e8bcca","tid":1234303,"uid":197178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"普選"},{"pid":"b092005f103df4cf045323e2580d9d4c4a04ea0a","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"起碼一星期！挨多一次 目標G20"},{"pid":"9c7e02b1d667d120b028a8110f92d73259b615e6","tid":1234303,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"